Instructions for installing and running rocHPL!
1. Go to working folder (you should find rocHPL from there already installed, if not follow steps 2-x)
2. install: git clone https://github.com/ROCm/rocHPL.git
3. create following bash script: 

#!/bin/bash

# Build inside subshell:
(
        module load cce
        module load PrgEnv-cray
        module load craype-x86-rome
        module cray-mpich
        module load craype-accel-amd-gfx90a

        mpi_root=$CRAY_MPICH_DIR

        # Use cray wrapper:
        export CXX=CC
        export HIPCXX=CC

       ./install.sh --with-mpi=$mpi_root 
)
4. run build script: bash rochpl_build
